        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> tomato & mozzarella tortelloni with creamy 'Nduja & pepper sauce </strong>and top with the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
